codex
I’ve confirmed the defect mechanism in the harness: both synthesizers call the same fixed reference constructor, so changing only the noise RNG seed never changed the PN sequence or its delay. I’m separating reference identity from noise seeding, adding a distinct-sequence co-channel study, and adding an explicit same-code/different-delay multipath measurement. I’ll add Wilson 95% binomial intervals while leaving every existing detection count and probability untouched.
